  <summary date="2017-01-10T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Tax Free Health Insurance Act of 2017

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow an individual taxpayer a deduction from gross income of insurance premiums paid for the health care coverage of the taxpayer and the taxpayer's spouse and dependents. The bill makes the deduction available whether or not the taxpayer itemizes other deductions.</summary>
